ed="T" n="0787a05"/><persName key="A003890">釋慧稜</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000012815">杭州海鹽</placeName>人也，俗姓<name>孫</name>氏。初誕纏紫<lb
ed="T" n="0787a06"/>色胎衣<ptr target="#n269"/>。為童齓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g280"/>日，俊朗抗節<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1643"/>，於<placeName key="PL000000009882">吳苑通玄<lb
ed="T" n="0787a07"/>寺</placeName>登戒。已聞南方有禪學，遂遊<placeName key="PL000000056178">閩</placeName>嶺，謁<persName key="A003677">雪<lb
ed="T" n="0787a08"/>峯</persName>，提耳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1597"/>指訂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g65"/>，頓明本性。乃述偈云：「昔時謾<lb
ed="T" n="0787a09"/>向途中學，今日看來火裏氷。」如是親依，不<lb
ed="T" n="0787a10"/>下峯頂，計三十許載。冥循定業，謹攝矜莊。<lb
ed="T" n="0787a11"/><placeName key="PL000000017906">泉州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A003761">王延彬</persName>召<persName key="A003890">稜</persName>住<placeName key="PL000000017888">昭慶院</placeName>，禪子委輸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1118"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0787a12"/>唯虞後至。及於<placeName key="PL000000017164">長樂府</placeName>，居<placeName key="PL000000017203">長慶院</placeName>，二十餘<lb
ed="T" n="0787a13"/>年，出世不減一千五百眾。<persName key="A003890">稜</persName>性地慈忍，不妄<lb
ed="T" n="0787a14"/>許人。能反三隅<ptr target="#n939"/>，方加印可。以<date key="j20616452061645" when-iso="+0932-06-28">長興三年壬<lb
ed="T" n="0787a15"/>辰五月十七日</date>長往，春秋七十九，僧臘六十。<lb
ed="T" n="0787a16"/><placeName key="PL000000017164">閩</placeName>國<persName key="A006594">王</persName>氏私誄之「大師」，號<persName key="A003890">超覺</persName>。塔葬皆出<lb
ed="T" n="0787a17"/>官供。判官<persName key="A010697">林文盛</persName>為碑紀德云。</p>
